{"title_page": "1996 in UFC", "text_new": "{{short description|UFC MMA events in 1996}}\n{{Year in UFC\n|name = 1996 in UFC\n|image = Logo of the Ultimate Fighting Championship (1993-1999).png\n|image_size = 176px\n|first_date = February 16, 1996\n|last_date = December 7, 1996\n|total_events = 5\n|numbered_events = 4\n|total_fights = 43\n|title_fights = 2\n|preceded_by = [[1995 in UFC]]\n|followed_by = [[1997 in UFC]]\n}}\n\nThe year '''1996''' is the 4th year in the history of the [[Ultimate Fighting Championship]] (UFC), a [[mixed martial arts]] promotion based in the United States. In 1996 the UFC held 5 events beginning with, ''UFC 8: David vs. Goliath''.\n\n{{TOClimit|2}}\n\n==Title fights==\n{{MMAtitle}}\n{{MMAtitle card|[[List of UFC champions|Title fights in 1996]]}}\n{{MMAtitle bout\n| \n| [[Ken Shamrock]] (c)\n| def.\n| [[Kimo Leopoldo]]\n| submission (kneebar)\n| \n| 4:24\n| [[UFC 8]]\n| For The [[List of UFC champions#Superfight Championship|UFC Superfight Championship]].\n}}\n{{MMAtitle bout\n| \n| [[Dan Severn]]\n| def.\n| [[Ken Shamrock]] (c)\n| split decision\n| \n| 30:00\n| [[UFC 9]]\n| For The [[List of UFC champions#Superfight Championship|UFC Superfight Championship]].\n}}\n{{MMAtitle end|notes = yes}}\n\n==Debut UFC fighters==\n\nThe following fighters fought their first UFC fight in 1996:\n\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-break}}\n*Amaury Bitetti\n*[[Brian Johnston (Fighter)|Brian Johnston]]\n*Dave Berry\n*Dieusel Berto\n*[[Don Frye]]\n*[[Fabio Gurgel]]\n*Felix Mitchell\n*[[Gary Goodridge]]\n*Jack Nilson\n*[[Jerry Bohlander]]\n{{col-break}}\n*[[Joe Moreira]]\n*John Campetella\n*Julian Sanchez\n*Keith Mielke\n*[[Koji Kitao]]\n*[[Mark Coleman]]\n*[[Mark Schultz (amateur wrestler)|Mark Schultz]]\n*Matt Andersen\n*Moti Horenstein\n*Paul Herrera\n{{col-break}}\n*Rafael Carino\n*Reza Nasri\n*[[Roberto Traven]]\n*Sam Adkins\n*Sam Fulton\n*[[Scott Ferrozzo]]\n*Scott Fiedler\n*Steve Nelmark\n*Tai Bowden\n*Thomas Ramirez\n{{col-end}}\n\n==Events List==\n{{Main|List of UFC events}}\n\n{| class=\"sortable wikitable succession-box\" style=\"font-size:90%;\"\n! scope=\"col\" | #\n! scope=\"col\" | Event\n! scope=\"col\" | Date\n! scope=\"col\" | Venue\n! scope=\"col\" | Location\n! scope=\"col\" | Attendance\n|-\n|013\n|[[Ultimate Ultimate 1996|UFC The Ultimate Ultimate 2]]\n|{{dts|1996|Dec|7}}\n|[[Fair Park Arena]]\n|[[Birmingham, Alabama]], U.S.\n|{{nts|6000}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tapology.com/fightcenter/events/ufc-115-ultimate-ultimate-1996|title=UFC 11.5: Ultimate Ultimate 1996|publisher=tapology.com|accessdate=Oct 20, 2010}}</ref>\n|-\n|012\n|{{sort|UFC 011|[[UFC 11|UFC 11: The Proving Ground]]}}\n|{{dts|1996|Sep|20}}\n|[[Augusta-Richmond County Civic Center|Augusta Civic Center]]\n|[[Augusta, Georgia]], U.S.\n|{{nts|4500}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://sports.yahoo.com/mma/news?slug=ki-ufcelevn041309|title=UFC 11: Coleman by default|publisher=sports.yahoo.com|accessdate=Oct 19, 2010}}</ref>\n|-\n|011\n|{{sort|UFC 010|[[UFC 10|UFC 10: The Tournament]]}}\n|{{dts|1996|Jul|12}}\n|[[Fair Park Arena]]\n|[[Birmingham, Alabama]], U.S.\n|{{nts|4300}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tapology.com/fightcenter/events/ufc-10-the-tournament|title=UFC 10: The Tournament|publisher=tapology.com|accessdate=Oct 20, 2010}}</ref>\n|-\n|010\n|{{sort|UFC 009|[[UFC 9|UFC 9: Motor City Madness]]}}\n|{{dts|1996|May|17}}\n|[[Cobo Arena]]\n|[[Detroit]], [[Michigan]], U.S.\n|{{nts|10000}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tapology.com/fightcenter/events/ufc-9-motor-city-madness|title=UFC 9: Motor City Madness|publisher=tapology.com|accessdate=Oct 20, 2010}}</ref>\n|-\n|009\n|{{sort|UFC 008|[[UFC 8|UFC 8: David vs. Goliath]]}}\n|{{dts|1996|Feb|16}}\n|[[Coliseo Rub\u00e9n Rodr\u00edguez]]\n|[[Bayam\u00f3n, Puerto Rico|Bayam\u00f3n]], Puerto Rico\n|{{nts|13000}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tapology.com/fightcenter/events/ufc-8-david-vs-goliath|title=UFC 8: David vs. Goliath|publisher=tapology.com|accessdate=Oct 20, 2010}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==See also==\n* [